Package edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans

Class AbstractTestPlan

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.test_plans.AbstractTestPlan
Direct Known Subclasses:
FailingTestList, TestPlan
public abstract class AbstractTestPlan extends Object
Represents a test plan in the SystemTestPlan system. There are two main types of test plans, normal test plans associated with a named project under development where test cases can be added to the end of the list and the failing test list that holds test cases from across all test plans that are currently failing.
Author:
Kevin John, Jordan Robertson
